 Đào</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-L%E1%BB%97-V%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0-t%E1%BA%A1p-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87t-v%E1%BA%ADn-Ng%C3%B4-cung-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-FiBx5Vy7dbUb219bNSbXfw">Phụng hoạ Lỗ Vọng nhàn cư tạp đề - Điệt vận Ngô cung từ - 奉和魯望閑居雜題—迭韻吳宮詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/author-YaU63-B8n1CAEl8OjKg7AQ">Bì Nhật Hưu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Qu%C3%A1-H%E1%BB%93-B%E1%BA%AFc/poem-UJ9fPHjVQ_7NAbTh9MJpeA">Quá Hồ Bắc - 過湖北</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/Thi%C3%AAn-thu-gi%C3%A1m-ph%C3%BA/poem-aNFJrxFI6pAICUyX7CKLvQ">Thiên thu giám phú - 千秋鑑賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/author-EY3eHTvDpkwLbISMoUQtYg">Phạm Tông Mại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Lu%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%C4%83ng-l%C3%A2u-h%E1%BB%AFu-ho%C3%A0i/poem-EQ8PQkJfxTbrYGtG0BuRkA">Xuân nhật đăng lâu hữu hoài - 春日登樓有懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Lu%C3%A2n/author-VVZ_VDVd2wfprGEnIm6L6g">Lư Luân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
